data.description: This is a DIAMOND IN THE ROUGH and an EXCELLENT investment opportunity! A 5 STAR VRBO and a SUPERHOST Airbnb rating!!! The front unit is a cozy 2 bedroom, 1 bath unit fully remodeled and currently booked out from now through March and getting more bookings daily. The 1 bedroom, 1 bath rear studio unit is rented by a long term tenant who would prefer not to move (and actually oversees the front unit.)  Keep it as an Airbnb/VRBO or live in the front unit. ZONED R-5 , you could add on more units or scrape what's there and build a multiplex building. Don't wait or you may be too late!
